# Data Dictionary — maddi2024 (IO₂, no executable code)

Original: Publons (reviewer-report word counts) matched to Web of Science (citations), 2009–2020, N=57,482.
DATA STATUS: Publons access has changed since 2024; the raw data is NOT available in this package.
No raw_data file is provided. You have only this documentation.

Variables:
